<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1007600' id='t-1007600'>But we can't find that</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1010200' id='t-1010200'>unless we know what we're looking for.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1012280' id='t-1012280'>We have to do our work on ourself,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1014400' id='t-1014400'>be intentional about that,
