<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1025920' id='t-1025920'>Things would start to change.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:19
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1028800' id='t-1028800'>And as we finish up,
