<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1038480' id='t-1038480'>Discover that, live it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1040760' id='t-1040760'>not just for you,
but for everybody around you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1044400' id='t-1044400'>because that is what starts
to change the world.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1047280' id='t-1047280'>What is the work you can't not do?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:41
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1050400' id='t-1050400'>Thank you guys.</span>
</span>
</p>
